OL,3,CAbbington thought 'long and hard'
OL,4,Cbefore making Strictly complaint
OL,6,FThe 50-year-old, who left the show
OL,7,Fearly in 2023, said she thought "long
OL,8,Fand hard" before making a complaint to
OL,9,Fthe BBC about the behaviour of former
OL,10,Fdance partner Giovanni Pernice due to
OL,11,Fthe "backlash" she would receive.
OL,13,FPernice, who has rejected "any
OL,14,Fsuggestion of abusive or threatening
OL,15,Fbehaviour", will not return to the
OL,16,Fshow this year, and said in a
OL,17,Fstatement on Instagram in June that he
OL,18,Fis "cooperating fully" with an ongoing
OL,19,F"BBC investigation".
