OL,6,FSpeaking to the Sun On Sunday, the
OL,7,FSherlock actor said: "I found
OL,8,FGiovanni's behaviour unnecessary,
OL,9,Fabusive, cruel and mean. I couldn't
OL,10,Fsit back and let him do that to other
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,F"I had to think long and hard about
OL,14,Fmaking a complaint because I knew the
OL,15,Fbacklash I would get. But I would not
OL,16,Fhave been able to live with myself for
OL,17,Ffuture people going on that show.
