OL,7,Fin May, Pernice said he rejected the
OL,8,Faccusations and wanted to clear his
OL,9,Fname.
OL,11,F"Those who have followed my journey on
OL,12,FStrictly Come Dancing over the last
OL,13,Fdecade will know that I am passionate
OL,14,Fand competitive," wrote the 33-year-
OL,15,Fold, who has been a professional on
OL,16,Fthe dancing show since 2015.
OL,18,F"No-one is more ambitious for my dance
OL,19,Fpartners than me.
